        </p>
        <p>
          Each job, bounty, and hackathon strengthens the network of free professionals shaping their
          nation's digital future.
        </p>
        <div class="highlight-box movement-highlight">
          <p>A free, decentralized, and borderless economy for Cuba's next generation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="lp-cta-section">
